# Bitrix24 Rules

## API Access

- All Bitrix calls go through `lib/bitrix/client.ts` — never inline `fetch` to the Bitrix URL
- If unsure about the API shape, check `lib/bitrix/client.ts` before adding new methods
- NEVER expose the Bitrix webhook URL in client-side code

## Lead Sync

- Form submit creates a Lead row AND calls `crm.lead.add`
- Store returned Bitrix id on the Lead as `bitrix_lead_id`
- Lead must keep `session_id` for attribution back to Visit / Profile

## Webhooks

- Endpoint: `/app/api/webhooks/bitrix/`
- Verify shared secret header on every request
- On `ONCRMDEALUPDATE` with stage WON: find Lead by `bitrix_lead_id` and mark converted
